    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "PAA\nConquest\nof the Pacific\nMAY 1935\nNAVY MASS FLIGHT\nHAWAII TO MIDWAY ISLAND AND RETURN\nAAMC 10$1234\nCOVER CARRIED ON FLEET MANEUVERS INVOLVING FIVE NAVY PATROL\nSOLADRONS AND 43 AIRCRAFT BETWEEN PEARL HARBOR AND MIDWAY Is.\nWITH STOP-OVER AT FRENCH FRIGATE SHORLS. COVER SHOWN DISPATCHED\nFROMA MIDWAY AN MAY 23 VIA PATROL SQUADRON FOUR, ARRIVING AT\nPEARL HARBOR ON MAY 24 (BACKSTAMP).",
